{
  "texts": [
    "The average of importance metrics of model i, ϕ i τ 's, across all tasks is the overall model importance metric of the model i:",
    "where T represents a collection of all possible forecasting tasks, and |T | indicates its cardinality.",
    "We note that the weight for a subset in Eq.",
    "(6) is calculated in the same manner as in the Shapley value formula in Eq.",
    "(5) that is the weighted average over all possible permutations of coalitions."
  ]
}